### Polymarket Order API Tests
### Make sure the API is running: python run_api.py

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Active Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders

### Get Orders by Token ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?token_id=YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE

### Market Sell Position (Sell All)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/sell/market
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "amount": null,
  "order_type": "FOK"
}

### Market Sell Position (Specific Amount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/sell/market
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "amount": 10.0,
  "order_type": "FOK"
}

### Limit Sell Position
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/sell/limit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "price": 0.55,
  "amount": 10.0,
  "order_type": "GTC"
}

### Limit Sell Position (Sell All)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/sell/limit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "price": 0.60,
  "amount": null,
  "order_type": "GTC"
}

### Market Buy Position
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/buy/market
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "amount": 10.0,
  "order_type": "FOK"
}

### Limit Buy Position
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/buy/limit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token_id": "YOUR_TOKEN_ID_HERE",
  "price": 0.45,
  "amount": 10.0,
  "order_type": "GTC"
}

### Claim Rewards
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/rewards/claim
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "condition_id": "YOUR_CONDITION_ID_HERE",
  "amounts": [10.0, 5.0]
}

### Cancel Specific Order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "YOUR_ORDER_ID_HERE"
}

### Cancel All Orders
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/orders/cancel/all
